entry.title: Russia Launches Missile Volley Across Ukraine
entry.content: Moscow unleashed a fresh barrage of missiles across Ukraine, with strikes on critical infrastructure cutting off water supplies in the capital and causing power outages in the west of the country, authorities said.

entry.title: China Is Investing Billions in Pakistan. Its Workers There Are Under Attack.
entry.content: Beijing’s Belt and Road investment strategy meets resistance in the developing world it seeks to influence.

entry.title: Conservatism Grows in Brazil, Despite Leftist President
entry.content: Conservative politicans backed by a wealthy agricultural sector cement their presence in Congress, churches and commerce despite right-wing President Bolsonaro’s election loss
